        span Your ultimate go on travel and tour solution
      .top-right
        i.fa-solid.fa-earth-africa.earth
        .location
          span Our Physical Offices
          p Mombasa, Nairobi, Naivasha
          i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-right

    .footer-bottom
      .footer-links
        .footer-link
          h4 Services
          p Budget Tours
          p Expert Insights
          p Independent
          p Luxury Tours
